column25: 占位符，用于表示每一格对应的语言

column2: This is the moveable button, press shift+left mouse button to move\nClick the left mouse button again to determine the position\nRight mouse button to reset the position
column10: 这是可移动按钮，按shift+鼠标左键可以移动\n再点击一次鼠标左键确定位置\n鼠标右键重置位置
已添加到你的物品栏中

column2: This is the search box\nRight click to clear the text
column10: 这是搜索框\n支持拼音搜索，拼音声母搜索，拼音首字母搜索和三者混合搜索\n按下鼠标右键清空文本

column2: Enabling it will turn on fuzzy search
column10: 启用后将开启模糊搜索

column2: When enabled it will append the search spell ID
column10: 启用后会附加搜索法术ID

column2: has been removed from the favorites

Help
Ctrl+left click on a spell will put it directly into the inventory
Shift+left click on a spell will put it into the held wand
Alt+left click on a spell will put it into the favorite,
and if you perform this action in the favorite, you are deleting the spell from the favorite.
column10:
帮助
对一个法术按下ctrl+鼠标左键会直接放入背包
如果是shift+鼠标左键是放入手持法杖
对一个法术按下alt+鼠标左键会放入收藏中，
如果在收藏中执行此操作则是在收藏中删除此法术

column2: Click to fix the current wand and window\nShortcut ~/`(GRAVE) to fix current wand and window
column10: 点击固定当前法杖和窗口\n快捷键 ~ 固定法杖和窗口

column2: Click to unfix the wand and window\nShortcut ~/`(GRAVE) to unfix current wand and window
column10: 点击取消固定法杖和窗口\n快捷键 ~ 取消固定法杖和窗口

column2: Right click will disable the spell placement on the ground feature, \nwhich prevents accidental touches
column10: 右键将禁止法术放置在地上功能，\n可防误触

column2: Right click will enable spell placement on the ground function
column10: 右键将开启法术放置在地上功能

column2:
Help:
Hold shift and left click on a grid to select
While holding shift down, left click on another grid to perform a box-select operation
Click on one side of the highlight box while holding shift to deselect it.
Ctrl+left click after selecting one or more squares allows you to move them.
Backspace to delete a spell
Hold down alt and left click to promote spell to Always Cast
column10:
帮助:
按住shift点击一个格子可以选择
按住shift的时候再点击另一个格子进行框选操作
按住shift的时候点击框选格的一边取消选择
选择了一个或多个格子之后按下ctrl键可以对其进行移动
退格键删除法术
按住alt键点击一个法术让其变成始终

column2: Shift+left click copy properties into the spawner\nleft click to copy the wand to the player's position
column10: 按住shift点击复制属性进生成器\n直接点击复制法杖到玩家位置

column2: Wand Box\nPress the right click to switch to historical editing data
column10: 法杖仓库\n按下右键切换为历史编辑数据

column2: Wand History Edit\nPress the right click to switch to Wand Box
column10: 法杖历史编辑数据\n按下右键切换为法杖仓库

column2: Sure you want to clear the history, it can't be recovered!
column10: 确定要清空历史吗，清空后无法恢复！

column2:
Help
After clicking on the highlight to select a wand 
Hold the ctrl to click on another wand to swap positions
Wand with pin cannot be deleted
Cross-page swap is not supported
Wand History Edit does not support swapping and pin
column10:
帮助
在点击高亮选择了一个格子之后
按住ctrl键点击另一个格子可以交换法杖位置
有图钉的法杖不能删除
不支持跨页交换
历史编辑数据不支持交换功能和图钉功能

column2: Holy shit, you managed to create 99,999 pages. Is your computer okay? You can't create any more pages.

column2: Not checking for updates, click to check for updates
The current version is the latest version
New version: $0\nCurrent version: $1\nClick to automatically download the new version of the zip
column10: 新版本:$0\n当前版本:$1\n点击自动下载新版压缩包

column2: The new version has been downloaded. You can go to the Check for updates button to copy the download path.

column2: Download failed, Click retry\nIt may be caused by network problems.
column10: 下载失败，点击重试\n可能是由于网络问题或者GFW造成的

column2: Request connection failed\nIt may be caused by network problems.\nClick Recheck
column10: 请求失败\n可能是由于网络问题或者GFW造成的\n点击重新检查

column2: Leave the laboratory\nRight click to reset the lab
column10: 离开实验室\n右键重置实验室

column2: You are not near the lab and cannot reset
column10: 你不在实验室附近，不能重置

column2: Teleport to cursor\nPress the throw button (default right mouse button) to teleport, Hold to teleport continuously\nWhen turned on, you cannot throw items. Pressing shift will temporarily turn off this function and allow throwing.
column10: 传送到光标\n按下投掷键(默认鼠标右键)传送，长按连续传送\n开启后无法投掷物品，按下shift会临时关闭此功能并允许投掷

column2: Disable Wand Editing Historical Data Collection\nCollection may cause lag, which can be alleviated by close

Disable Edit Box Spell Hover Info

column10: 按下 +/-或 方向键左/右键 +1/-1，长按会连续执行。\n按住shift执行上述操作将乘以十。

column10: 此操作不可撤销，再点击一次确认
